    {
        "content": "<p>I just opened <a href=\"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/pull/20479\">#20479</a> which proves that <code>Set.Ioc (0 : ℝ) r</code> cannot be compact for positive <code>r</code> (edit: <a href=\"https://leanprover-community.github.io/mathlib4_docs/find/?pattern=isCompact_Ioc_iff#doc\">docs#isCompact_Ioc_iff</a>)</p>",
